title: Dylan O’Brien on Jake Gyllenhaal Comparisons in All Too Well Short
author: extratv
description: ‘Extra’s’ Cheslie Kryst talks with Dylan O’Brien, who is starring in Taylor Swift’s short film ‘All Too Well.’ At the NYC premiere of the short, Dylan shared his take on those Jake Gyllenhaal comparisons, as well as what it was like to work with Taylor.
